org.gvsig.tools.swing.api

Class ToolsSwingLocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.tools.locator.AbstractLocator
      • org.gvsig.tools.locator.BaseLocator
        • org.gvsig.tools.swing.api.ToolsSwingLocator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Locator, Locator_withExists

    public class ToolsSwingLocator
extends BaseLocator
    Locator for the tools swing Library. It returns a reference to the library's main utilities.
